org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulator.mutable

Interface PotionEffectData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataManipulator<PotionEffectData,ImmutablePotionEffectData>, DataSerializable, ListData<PotionEffect,PotionEffectData,ImmutablePotionEffectData>, ValueContainer<PotionEffectData>

    public interface PotionEffectData
extends ListData<PotionEffect,PotionEffectData,ImmutablePotionEffectData>
    Represents a List of PotionEffects that can be applicable to various DataHolders such as Entitys, ItemStacks as ItemTypes.POTION, etc.
